original_title: Wノーパン家政婦羞恥 竹下千晶 矢部寿恵
overview: Popular beautiful mature women, Hisae Yabe & Chiaki Takeshita, co-star for the first time! Hisae and Chiaki, who work at the same housekeeper dispatch company, are aiming for the "Kato family" that they will be in charge of this time. It's not normal for two veterans to form a pair, but this time there seems to be a reason... The reason for this is that the two sons of the Kato family have been forced to quit their job as housekeepers because of various mischief. The two enthusiastically said, "If it's a child's prank, we'll beat it!"
title: Double Shameful Commando Maids – Chiaki Takeshita Hisae Yabe
